OL,5, A public apology will be given to      
OL,6, victims and survivors of Historical    
OL,7, Institutional Abuse (HIA) in Northern  
OL,8, Ireland later on Friday.               
OL,10,FFive Stormont ministers will each offer
OL,11,Fan apology on behalf of the government.
OL,13,FThe long-awaited apology was           
OL,14,Frecommended following an inquiry, which
OL,15,Freported back in 2017.                 
OL,17,FApologies will also be delivered by    
OL,18,Frepresentatives from six institutions  
OL,19,Fthat ran facilities where abuse took   
OL,20,Fplace.                                 
